Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:03.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:07.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make sure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:13.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:16.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our full-on conflict with Phantom Lord had begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:21.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the middle of it Lucy was captured, and the master lost his magical powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:22.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:25.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we managed to rescue Lucy somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:29.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for even more who-knows-what!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:41.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to mystery is right in front of us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:44.10,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole world's a wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:47.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,which we're already wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:52.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This excitement gets my heart racing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:56.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:59.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,What is real, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:03.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I see tomorrow, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:10.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The only part leveling up is my curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:15.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just throw away our daily life together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:23.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! S. O. W.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:29.27,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Living itself will be our training!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:32.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:35.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search for even more who-knows-what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:40.82,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be satisfied with just the normal answers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:43.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This magical wonder life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:46.45,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Our future is wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:51.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do our best living our life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:53.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,the way we want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:56.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:08.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that an old friend of the master lives in a tree house in Magnolia East Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:15.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A healing wizard named Poluchka, she hates humans, so she lives alone deep in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:20.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However they say she's a specialist in healing wounds from magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:24.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the master has been carried there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:33.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to the master, I mean, the sick person!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:37.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This happened because he was too reckless for his age.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:40.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, what a fool you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:42.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you plan to stay here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:43.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, but... with the master in this condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:48.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let us care for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:49.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:54.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The stench of fretting faces is the greatest poison to a sick man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:59.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from wind magic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:02.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the work of the magic, Drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:07.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A fearful magic that forces your opponent's magical power to flow out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The drained magical power drifts off into the air and soon dissipates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:16.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we could gather Makarov's lost magical power,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that would speed his recovery, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:21.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already too late. His recovery will be prolonged...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:23.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:25.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will inform everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}still{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:31.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you didn't want us to stay and listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:34.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the smell of humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:36.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:38.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been such a handful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:52.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For a wizard, their magical power is the source of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:56.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And for one with great magical power, the suffering increases in kind. {nice wording!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:04:02.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't keep fighting, you may die like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:07.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are such a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,15 Minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:23.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we had to retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we didn't get revenge for the guild and Levy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:27.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is their headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:34.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we attack them with ranged magic from the high ground to the southwest...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:39.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I'll bring explosive lacrima with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:43.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring out a stack of powerful magic books for holder-type wizards from the warehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:48.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Still uneasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:54.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:01.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:05.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's the fate of rich heiress' to get chased.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:09.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the ones who protect them are Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:15.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm really surprised. Why did you keep it a secret, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:19.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to hide anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:23.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After I ran away from home, I didn't really want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:29.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For a full year, he never showed any interest in his runaway daughter. And now he wants me back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:33.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My father went to such terrible lengths to take me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:35.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:42.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you get down to it, it's originally my fault for running away from home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:45.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! Your father's the bad guy here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:46.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:49.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:56.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to my selfish actions, I've caused all this trouble for everyone. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:01.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess if I went home, it would end this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:08.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But "rich heiress" just doesn't strike the right tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:12.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laughing in this dirty old beer hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:15.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and making a ruckus while on some adventure... That's the Lucy I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to stay here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:24.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of returning someplace you don't want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:28.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Lucy of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:32.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your home to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:40.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, sheesh... You're stronger than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Men are weak to tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:07:00.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... I can't tell where Mystogan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:07.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If their aim is Lucy, then they'll be attacking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:10.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a lot of injured people... This doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master is gravely wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:15.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't know where Mystogan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:18.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one we can rely on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:23.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's in a crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:28.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves the old codger right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:32.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't have anything to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handle it yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus... Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:38.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:44.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man started this war. Why should I be the one to bail him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:47.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're targeting Lucy... One of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:49.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:52.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean the newbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:56.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her I'll be happy to save her if she becomes my woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:01.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Is that any way to speak to someone you're asking help from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:07.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And tell the old man to hurry up and retire, so I can take over his position as master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:25.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that person actually a member of Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:29.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:35.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy was captured even though I was there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:38.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. You'll get in everyone's way as you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:41.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you once were an S class wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:53.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The master is absent. No Laxus, Mystogan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:59.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be impossible to continue the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had gone with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:33.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The shame! This is my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:12.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their guild is walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:22.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't predict this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:31.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This{\i0} is how they attack us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Focusing Cannon, Jupiter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:47.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:13.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:17.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! Everyone, take cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:34.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:35.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She requipped?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:42.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:46.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you touch the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Adamantine Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:50.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't intend to actually block it, does she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:53.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how much crazy defensive power that armor gives you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:56.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Erza! You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:04.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! All we can do is believe in her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:20.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:53.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She stopped it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She saved our butts, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:15.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now Erza as well. Both are out of commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:21.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You no longer have a chance for victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:24.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over Lucy Heartfilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not on your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:30.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we a guild that hands over our friends? I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:33.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy is one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand her over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:52.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:56.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd rather die than sell out our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our answer will never change, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:31.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll get a second extra-large helping of Jupiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:35.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiver in fear for the 15 minutes it takes to charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:38.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna shoot it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:42.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:43.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:47.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Erza's magic was the only reason we survived the first shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are their forces coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:56.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't they supposed to fire Jupiter again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:56.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:59.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare into the pits of hell, Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:02.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You only have two choices left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:05.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be destroyed by my troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:07.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or be blown away by Jupiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:11.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He plans on blowing up his own allies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a bluff! They won't shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:19.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Jose's magic, Shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're phantom soldiers that Jose created.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:25.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Shade...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:26.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something about Jupiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bust it to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:33.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,15 minutes, right? Let me at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:35.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:42.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman, we're going in too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:43.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:45.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make a stand here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:46.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:47.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:50.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:56.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a safe house. Stay there until the battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to fight alongside everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault this happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one thinks that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:08.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For our fallen comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For our guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:15.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone takes pride in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:18.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So listen to what I say, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:24.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reedus, take Lucy to the safehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:25.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oui.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:31.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:32.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oui!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:37.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not have the power to fight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:39.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will protect my friends, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:47.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,14 minutes until Jupiter fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:03.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? My strength is being drained...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:04.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:06.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, these couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:09.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful! They're cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:15.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom soldiers where just a touch will sap away your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Shade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:18.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So just don't touch 'em, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we can shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guns Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunlight Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bisca, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya! {this is in the script in english}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:33.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good one there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:40.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They came back to life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:52.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:55.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no end to this, will there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:58.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:01.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this terrible feeling I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Not even a dent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:20.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to destroy it from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:24.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:33.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:40.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,11 minutes until Jupiter fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a lacrima for concentrating magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:46.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a lacrima that big before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:52.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Magic Focusing Cannon is a weapon that uses concentrated magic power instead of a cannon shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:56.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but all I need to do is break it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:58.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:18:59.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A lookout?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:02.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever! I'll just get rid of anyone in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:08.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for this! Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:11.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:13.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, my body is... on its own...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:20.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like... you're the one getting in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:25.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,10 minutes until Jupiter fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:41.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down, Bisca.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:43.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to protect the guild at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:49.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys don't understand the pain of losing your comrades, or the suffering having your guild destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:52.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let people like that take our guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only 9 minutes until Jupiter's next shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:13.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it. I'm going to smash that giant crystal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:17.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can break that lacrima, Jupiter shouldn't be able to fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:23.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,7 minutes until Jupiter fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:27.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to stand around blabbing at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:34.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:37.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:38.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:44.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! We don't have time for you to fight this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:46.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to hurry and destroy Jupiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:49.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:50.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:05.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,6 minutes until Jupiter fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:10.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Totomaru, and I manipulate the element of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:14.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of those whatchamacalit-somethingorother 4?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:19.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, it's the Element 4! The only part you got right was the 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:22.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All flames are under my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:30.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether enemy or in nature, all flame is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:33.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My flames are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, who cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:39.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, destroy this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:43.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you drew a bad match-up, my little fire wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:02.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter is starting to activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:07.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,5 minutes until Jupiter fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:27.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:30.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:40.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,chasing after your profile left only in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:52.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You said, "I never want to see your face again," when you left me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:57.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But the tears on your cheek said it all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:03.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time you felt like you'd be swallowed up in the waves of contradiction
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:10.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,you always held back your tears, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:21.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"What a strong person," they said, but everyone overestimated you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:30.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and before you knew it you lost sight of who you really are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:34.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the sun I thought would always be near me collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:37.01,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and the light shut off...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:41.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubbing out the truths and the lies of one day, altogether
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:42.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:45.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:54.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,still, ironically, chasing after your profile in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:24:00.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a stupid reason to get into a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:03.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a man, then get some more passionate reason to fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:06.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you just sounded a lot like Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.28,0:24:07.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.30,0:24:08.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.17,0:24:10.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.92,0:24:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... That's even more like Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.81,0:24:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: So No One Sees the Tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.56,0:24:20.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get the way Elfman speaks out of my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:21.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, it must be love!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.26,0:24:23.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.76,0:24:26.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
